License discipline (intentional)
================================================================================

This capability deliberately does NOT import, vendor, or copy source from any
AGPL-3.0 component (uds-core, uds-cli, uds-common, maru-runner). It INTEROPERATES
with UDS Core by emitting/consuming UDS Package custom resources and by running
as a standard Pepr admission module — it does not link against AGPL source. This
keeps the SZL governance capability cleanly Apache-2.0.
